description: Another luxury rehab by Englewood Jack! Luxury living at it's finest! This magnificently rehabbed home located in West Englewood has all the amenities you need to create a comfortable and tranquil living space for you and your family. Featuring three full floors of living space, SEVEN large bedrooms, and three full baths, this house can accommodate a large family with ease. The two electric fireplaces (one located in the master suite) adds a nice touch and also helps to cut down on heating bills. With plenty of living space inside and outside, this property has a huge back and side yard. In addition to the beautiful inside of this property, no expense was spared on the outside as it has a new roof, gutters, AC unit, fencing and parking pad. The fresh tuckpoint gives the brown brick a beautiful finish. You will not be disappointed with this one.
